Title: The history of human interest in Trash
DateModified: '2019-02-25'
DatePublished: '2019-02-25'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/the-history-of-human-interest-in-trash
SetInCountry: Japan
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Juan Colombo
AuthorCountry: United States of America
Text: Insight perspective of the man-culture relationship with trash. A review of
  societal values and how these values shape younger generation and their relationship
  with chores at school, trash disposal, treatment and collection and adults. I would
  like to compare these values with other occidental cultures.
